	* src/totem.c: (on_window_key_press_event): If we have modifiers, and
	either Ctrl, Mod1 (Alt), or any of Mod3 to Mod5 (Mod2 is num-lock...)
	are pressed, we let Gtk+ handle the key (Closes: #104675)

